### start the server by `node server.js`

### Use Postman or Curl to test the APIs 

1. ### Initialize the database -
`http://localhost:5000/initialize` (GET Request)

2. ### Statistics API - 
 `http://localhost:5000/statistics/:{YEAR}-{MONTH}` (GET Request)
  eg.- `http://localhost:5000/statistics/:2022-07`

3. ### Bar Chart API - 
 `http://localhost:5000/bar-chart/:{YEAR}-{MONTH}` (GET Request)
  eg.- `http://localhost:5000/bar-chart/:2022-07`

4. ### Combined data API -
  `http://localhost:5000/combined-data?month={YEAR}-{MONTH}` (GET Request)
  eg.- `http://localhost:5000/combined-data?month=2022-07`
  